---
// Process section — 3-step timeline
---

<section
  id="proceso"
  class="min-h-[calc(100vh-56px)] py-8 flex flex-col justify-center bg-deep-navy relative overflow-hidden px-5 md:px-16 border-t border-b border-ice-cyan/10"
>
  <!-- Top gradient line -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-ice-cyan to-transparent opacity-30"
  ></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto relative z-10">
    <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-frost-white text-center mb-4">
      El Proceso DeepFrozen
    </h2>

    <div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4">
      <!-- Timeline connector line -->
      <div class="timeline-line hidden md:block opacity-50"></div>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-deep-navy border-2 border-ice-cyan flex items-center justify-center mb-3 z-10 text-ice-cyan shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,188,212,0.3)]"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[36px] w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">eco</span>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-frost p-4 rounded-xl w-full h-full flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
          <img
            src="/images/PROCESS_1-400.webp"
            srcset="/images/PROCESS_1-400.webp 400w, /images/PROCESS_1.webp 800w"
            sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw"
            alt="Materia prima fresca"
            width="800"
            height="434"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-3"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <h3 class="text-[22px] font-semibold text-ice-cyan mb-2">
            Paso 1: Materia Prima Real
          </h3>
          <p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-pale-blue">
            Seleccionamos ingredientes de la más alta calidad, preparados en su punto óptimo de
            frescura y sabor.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-deep-navy border-2 border-ice-cyan flex items-center justify-center mb-3 z-10 text-ice-cyan shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,188,212,0.3)]"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[36px] w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">ac_unit</span>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-frost p-4 rounded-xl w-full h-full flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
          <img
            src="/images/PROCESS_2-400.webp"
            srcset="/images/PROCESS_2-400.webp 400w, /images/PROCESS_2.webp 800w"
            sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw"
            alt="Ultracongelado y sellado al vacío"
            width="800"
            height="434"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-3"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <h3 class="text-[22px] font-semibold text-ice-cyan mb-2">
            Paso 2: Ultracongelado + Sellado
          </h3>
          <p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-pale-blue">
            Abatimos la temperatura rápidamente a -40°C y sellamos al vacío para bloquear el oxígeno y
            evitar la oxidación.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-deep-navy border-2 border-warm-copper flex items-center justify-center mb-3 z-10 text-warm-copper shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(199,123,63,0.5)]"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[36px] w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">local_dining</span>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-frost p-4 rounded-xl w-full h-full flex flex-col border-warm-copper/30 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
          <img
            src="/images/PROCESS_3-400.webp"
            srcset="/images/PROCESS_3-400.webp 400w, /images/PROCESS_3.webp 800w"
            sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw"
            alt="Resultado gourmet en casa"
            width="800"
            height="434"
            class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-3"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <h3 class="text-[22px] font-semibold text-warm-copper mb-2">
            Paso 3: Resultado Gourmet
          </h3>
          <p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-pale-blue">
            Directo del freezer al horno o sartén. Disfruta de un plato con calidad de restaurante en
            minutos.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>